Jacob Smith (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacob_Smith_(actor) 0 Jonathan Jacob Charles William Smith (b. January 21, 1990) is an American actor. He began his career as a young child, making several guest appearances on popular TV shows before being cast as Owen Salinger on Party of Five, a role he held for two years. After the series' end, Smith went onto appear in Phantom of the Megaplex, a Disney Channel Original Movie, in 2000 and then in Cheaper by the Dozen and its sequel, Cheaper by the Dozen 2, in 2003 and 2005.
